release_note: Binger is the easiest and most fun way of finding shows to watch with your partner. In this update we have added the French Library. This update includes bug fixes and performance improvements.
We ve updated the app to fix some crashes and make features load faster.
Behold! We ve added Disney to our library. Thousands of new series and movies to swipe on. Have fun and swipe away! Binger now supports Spanish.
We did a spring cleaning fixed some bugs and added an onboarding for new users. Enjoy and swipe away!
